Where do you feel the breath?

00:11:34.770 --> 00:11:40.980 align:middle line:10%
And just let the mind
very gently rest there.

00:11:40.980 --> 00:11:45.050 align:middle line:90%


00:11:45.050 --> 00:11:49.740 align:middle line:84%
