how we can take our natural
passions and interests

00:37:31.230 --> 00:37:33.060 align:middle line:90%
and use them to help the world.

00:37:33.060 --> 00:37:36.950 align:middle line:84%
Where false guidance
always is about separation.

00:37:36.950 --> 00:37:39.530 align:middle line:84%
It wants to make one person
better than the other.

00:37:39.530 --> 00:37:43.190 align:middle line:84%
In other words, you might
get an imagination that says,

00:37:43.190 --> 00:37:46.580 align:middle line:84%
this will elevate you above
others and make you the hero.

00:37:46.580 --> 00:37:48.320 align:middle line:84%
Now, true guidance
is going to give you

00:37:48.320 --> 00:37:52.520 align:middle line:84%
guidance that will ultimately
help you to have abundance.

00:37:52.520 --> 00:37:55.670 align:middle line:84%
