and fortune along with that.

00:37:55.670 --> 00:37:57.500 align:middle line:84%
But true guidance
would never ever

00:37:57.500 --> 00:37:59.840 align:middle line:84%
talk about that as
its central topic.

00:37:59.840 --> 00:38:03.390 align:middle line:84%
False guidance
also puts us down.

00:38:03.390 --> 00:38:04.340 align:middle line:90%
It's abusive.

00:38:04.340 --> 00:38:05.570 align:middle line:90%
It's critical.

00:38:05.570 --> 00:38:07.010 align:middle line:90%
And it makes us doubt ourself.

00:38:07.010 --> 00:38:09.715 align:middle line:84%
Where true guidance
is like a motivator.

00:38:09.715 --> 00:38:11.840 align:middle line:84%
It's like the greatest
coach in the world and says,

00:38:11.840 --> 00:38:12.640 align:middle line:90%
you can do it.

00:38:12.640 --> 00:38:15.035 align:middle line:84%
