00:39:57.290 --> 00:39:58.520 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:39:58.520 --> 00:40:01.160 align:middle line:84%
>> And is it ongoing
now, the conversation?

00:40:01.160 --> 00:40:03.350 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I mean, they
